            <section class="body-content col-sm-12 col-md-9 col-lg-9" id="main-content">
                    
                                      
                  
                       <div class="region region-content">
    <div data-drupal-messages-fallback class="hidden"></div>  <article class="node node--type-landing_page node--view-mode-full clearfix">
  
    

  <div>
      <div class="layout layout--threecol-25-50-25">
          <div  class="layout__region layout__region--top">
        <div class="block-region-top"><section data-block-plugin-id="entity_field:node:body" class="block block-ctools-block block-entity-fieldnodebody clearfix">
  
    

      
  <div class="field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-visually_hidden">
    <div class="field--label sr-only">Body</div>
              <div class="field--item"><p>The Inflation Reduction Act changed a wide range of tax laws and provided funds to improve our services and technology to make tax filing easier for you.</p>

<p>Since the Inflation Reduction Act is a 10-year plan, the changes won't happen immediately. We're working to implement the law as quickly as we can.&nbsp;</p>

<h2>Latest updates</h2>

<p>We'll share news on the latest developments here, so&nbsp;<strong>check back for updates.</strong></p>

<div class="accordion-list" data-fix-id="accordion1712674065134_805204">
<div class="table-responsive">
<div aria-multiselectable="true" class="panel-group accordion-list-group accordion-list-items" id="accordion1712674065134_805204" role="tablist">
<div class="collapsible-item panel panel-default" data-fix-id="Collapsible1720635892673_338723" id="Collapsible1720635892673_338723">
<div class="collapsible-item-heading panel-heading" id="headingCollapsible1720635892673_338723" role="tab">
<h4 class="collapsible-item-title panel-title" data-a11y-ignore="headerH2"><a aria-controls="collapseCollapsible1720635892673_338723" aria-expanded="false" class="collapsed collapsible-item-title-link" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseCollapsible1720635892673_338723" role="button"><span>Credit reporting changes</span></a></h4>
</div>

<div aria-labelledby="headingCollapsible1720635892673_338723" class="collapse collapsible-item-collapse panel-collapse" id="collapseCollapsible1720635892673_338723" role="tabpanel">
<div class="table-responsive">
<div class="collapsible-item-body panel-body">
<p><strong>Tax years 2023 and 2024 reporting relief: Forms 8835, Renewable Electricity Production Credit, and 3468, Investment Credit</strong></p>

<p>Under the Inflation Reduction Act, you’re required to file separate Forms 8835 and 3468 for each facility/property for which you claim a tax credit. IRS is aware of taxpayer concerns of the inability to import data into the forms.</p>

<p>For tax years 2023 and 2024, if you have more than 200 Forms 3468 or 200 Forms 8835, you can submit a single Form 3468 or Form 8835 with the aggregated credit amounts on the form. Attach a Portable Document Format (PDF) that contains all the required form information for each facility/property. Name the file “CleanEnergyRelief.pdf.” If you have multiple PDFs, add a sequential number to the end of the filename i.e. (“CleanEnergyRelief1.pdf” “CleanEnergyRelief2.pdf”). This relief also applies to shareholders or partners of passthrough entities.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="collapsible-item panel panel-default" data-fix-id="Collapsible1712674065137_464681" id="Collapsible1712674065137_464681">
<div class="collapsible-item-heading panel-heading" id="headingCollapsible1712674065137_464681" role="tab">
<h4 class="collapsible-item-title panel-title"><a aria-controls="collapseCollapsible1712674065137_464681" aria-expanded="false" class="collapsed collapsible-item-title-link" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseCollapsible1712674065137_464681" role="button">News releases</a></h4>
</div>

<div aria-labelledby="headingCollapsible1712674065137_464681" class="collapse collapsible-item-collapse panel-collapse" id="collapseCollapsible1712674065137_464681" role="tabpanel">
<div class="table-responsive">
<div class="collapsible-item-body panel-body">
<ul>
	<li>IR-2024-292, <a data-entity-substitution="canonical" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-uuid="3fc3d53d-0e1c-45dd-854b-00052fbe07fd" href="/newsroom/treasury-irs-finalize-more-partnership-clean-energy-regulations-and-propose-related-administrative-requirements" title="Treasury, IRS finalize more partnership clean energy regulations and propose related administrative requirements">Treasury, IRS finalize more partnership clean energy regulations and propose related administrative requirements</a></li>
	<li>IR-2024-281, <a data-entity-substitution="canonical" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-uuid="8a03da5a-80ad-477b-9cbb-3f4694357313" href="/newsroom/treasury-irs-issue-final-regulations-for-the-advanced-manufacturing-production-credit" title="Treasury, IRS issue final regulations for the Advanced Manufacturing Production Credit">Treasury, IRS issue final regulations for the Advanced Manufacturing Production Credit</a></li>
	<li>IR-2024-280, <a data-entity-substitution="canonical" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-uuid="486eb060-73d0-4442-967c-0ce37b18daf6" href="/newsroom/treasury-and-irs-issue-guidance-for-the-energy-efficient-home-improvement-credit" title="Treasury and IRS issue guidance for the Energy Efficient Home Improvement Credit">Treasury and IRS issue guidance for the Energy Efficient Home Improvement Credit</a></li>
	<li>IR-2024-277, <a data-entity-substitution="canonical" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-uuid="8d2a93b4-cd2e-4a34-b66a-3cfcef48104a" href="/newsroom/treasury-irs-grant-filing-exception-for-tax-exempt-organizations-from-filing-new-form-4626-alternative-minimum-tax-corporations" title="Treasury, IRS grant filing exception for tax-exempt organizations from filing new Form 4626, Alternative Minimum Tax - Corporations">Treasury, IRS grant filing exception for tax-exempt organizations from filing new Form 4626, Alternative Minimum Tax - Corporations</a></li>
	<li>IR-2024-275,&nbsp;<a data-entity-substitution="canonical" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-uuid="f0a63a76-7cad-4901-a444-f7a2df783859" href="/newsroom/irs-and-treasury-issue-guidance-on-implementation-of-advanced-manufacturing-investment-credit" title="IRS and Treasury issue guidance on implementation of advanced manufacturing investment credit">IRS and Treasury issue guidance on implementation of advanced manufacturing investment credit</a></li>
</ul>

<p><a data-entity-substitution="canonical" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-uuid="9ea0458d-f2b5-4228-8074-ce2d1f082747" href="/newsroom/news-on-the-inflation-reduction-act-of-2022" title="News on the Inflation Reduction Act of 2022">All news releases on the Inflation Reduction Act</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="collapsible-item panel panel-default" data-fix-id="Collapsible1712674065138_331106" id="Collapsible1712674065138_331106">
<div class="collapsible-item-heading panel-heading" id="headingCollapsible1712674065138_331106" role="tab">
<h4 class="collapsible-item-title panel-title"><a aria-controls="collapseCollapsible1712674065138_331106" aria-expanded="false" class="collapsed collapsible-item-title-link" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseCollapsible1712674065138_331106" role="button">Ready-to-use articles</a></h4>
</div>

<div aria-labelledby="headingCollapsible1712674065138_331106" class="collapse collapsible-item-collapse panel-collapse" id="collapseCollapsible1712674065138_331106" role="tabpanel">
<div class="table-responsive">
<div class="collapsible-item-body panel-body">
<ul>
	<li><a data-entity-substitution="canonical" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-uuid="940c2dfb-2e11-4e2a-ba46-6faa1c465412" href="/newsroom/irs-launches-new-energy-credits-online-tool" title="IRS launches new Energy Credits Online tool">IRS launches new Energy Credits Online tool</a></li>
