<h2>More information</h2>

<ul>
	<li><a data-entity-substitution="canonical" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-uuid="06d75d0f-2adc-4e9c-9ac8-3b80edd70e57" href="/about-irs/irs-inflation-reduction-act-strategic-operating-plan" title="IRS Inflation Reduction Act Strategic Operating Plan">Inflation Reduction Act Strategic Operating Plan</a></li>
</ul>

<h3>Laws and regulations</h3>

<ul>
	<li>
	<p><a data-entity-substitution="pup_linkit_media" data-entity-type="media" data-entity-uuid="1369d570-71ea-4531-92c5-4899c7f5c7bf" href="https://www.congress.gov/bill/117th-congress/house-bill/5376" title="Inflation Reduction Act of 2022 (H.R. 5376)">Inflation Reduction Act of 2022</a></p>
	</li>
</ul>

